# .gitignore for LaTeX projects

## Core auxiliary files
*.aux
*.lof
*.log
*.lot
*.fls
*.out
*.toc
*.fmt
*.fot
*.cb
*.cb2
.*.lb

## Bibliography
*.bbl
*.bcf
*.blg
*.run.xml

## Build tools
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex
*.synctex(busy)
*.synctex.gz
*.synctex.gz(busy)
*.pdfsync

## Indices
*.idx
*.ilg
*.ind
*.ist

## Nomenclature
*.nlo
*.nls

## Glossaries
*.acn
*.acr
*.alg
*.glg
*.glo
*.gls
*.glsdefs

## Beamer
*.nav
*.pre
*.snm
*.vrb

## Changes package
*.soc

## Latexian
TSWLatexianTemp*

## Listings
*.lol

## Hyperref
*.brf

## Tikz externalization
*.dpth
*.md5
*.auxlock

## PDF output (uncomment if you don't want to track PDFs)
*.pdf

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db